# __APP_PASCAL_NAME__

Standalone RadOS desktop shell generated by `@rdna/create`.

## Commands

- `pnpm install`
- `pnpm dev`
- `pnpm lint`
- `pnpm test`
- `pnpm build`

## Structure

- `lib/catalog.tsx` — App registry. Add your apps here.
- `components/Desktop.tsx` — Desktop shell with icons, windows, taskbar.
- `components/AppWindow.tsx` — Wraps the real `@rdna/radiants` AppWindow with store bindings.
- `components/Taskbar.tsx` — Start menu, volume, dark mode toggle.
- `store/` — Zustand store (windows + preferences).
- `hooks/` — `useWindowManager` for window actions, `useHashRouting` for URL sync.
